            Nobody said the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Nobel</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Committee</ENAMEX> was infallible. It did, after all, give <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Henry Kissinger</ENAMEX> the peace
prize in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1973</TIMEX>. But the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">folks</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Stockholm</ENAMEX> have traditionally been conservative
