<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">field</ENAMEX>. He got his share of bad press, for which I take--and am given--entirely
too much credit (read my <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">December 1986</TIMEX> feature story in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Discover</ENAMEX> by
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">clicking</ENAMEX> ). By <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1985</TIMEX>, when <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Prusiner</ENAMEX>'s own <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">papers</ENAMEX> were still suggesting that the
