            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Prusiner</ENAMEX>'s
boilerplate response to prion <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">critics</ENAMEX> has been that if mad-cow <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">disease</ENAMEX> or any
