<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">researchers</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">decades</TIMEX> to find culpable viruses--<ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">hepatitis</ENAMEX> C is a famous example.
