            Good science, not just <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Nobel</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Prize-caliber</ENAMEX> science, depends on hypothesis and test, and then the rigorous
demonstration that the preferred interpretation of the data was the only
