In the case of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Prusiner</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">prize</ENAMEX>, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Nobel Committee</ENAMEX> has settled for enthusiasm
